snippet.title: NEW GAME! DC TASK FORCE - DOWNLOAD!
snippet.description:
Download at zvitor.com
DC Task Force is a game where you explore the DC universe, visiting classic cities and planets, assembling your own Justice League team and recruiting members to protect planet Earth from an alien invasion. This campaign can be completed in just over an hour, but would require at least 7 hours to explore the entire universe and recruit all possible characters.
This game is free, like everything we've done here in the last 15 years, but I've only been able to dedicate so much time to all these projects thanks to the financial support of our supporters. Thank you very much and have fun!
